To run the development server apis, first installl Anaconda from:
https://www.continuum.io/downloads

To create a separeted environment run the command:
conda env create -f environment.yml

To activate the new environment run
source activate oga

More information on using conda see: http://conda.pydata.org/docs/using/envs.html

To run the apis run:
python manage.py runserver

to run tests run:
python manage.py tests
